</node>
<node id="&quot;CINNAMON ROLL&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"FOOD"</data>
  <data key="d1">"A cinnamon roll is a type of sweet roll similar to a doughnut but made with doughnut batter."&lt;SEP&gt;"Cinnamon Roll is a sweet roll commonly served in Northern Europe and North America, often enjoyed as a breakfast or dessert, featuring cinnamon and sugar flavors."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-a54a89950ff2fd3cb3d3a1223334b592&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-68cc9da7ccb381b782c583d3a72f9742</data>
</node>
