</node>
<node id="&quot;DABBY-DOUGHS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PRODUCT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Dabby-Doughs are a type of pastry traditionally made from leftover pie dough, filled with a mixture of cinnamon and sugar, and then baked."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-a54a89950ff2fd3cb3d3a1223334b592</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;PERSHING (DOUGHNUT)&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PRODUCT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Pershing is a type of doughnut that resembles a cinnamon roll but is made with doughnut batter and often covered with a sugar glaze or sprinkled with sugar and cinnamon."</data>
