</node>
<node id="&quot;CINNAMON SUGAR&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"INGREDIENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Cinnamon Sugar is a mixture of ground cinnamon and granulated sugar used as a topping or ingredient in various baked goods, including cinnamon rolls and dabby-doughs."&lt;SEP&gt;"Cinnamon sugar is a mixture of ground cinnamon and granulated sugar used as a spice for desserts."</data>
