</node>
<node id="&quot;WIENERBRØD&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PRODUCT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Wienerbrød is a type of bread commonly found in Denmark, and 'Kanelsnegl' is a specific form of it, known for its cinnamon and sugar flavor."</data>
