  <data key="d1">"Dit Da Jow is a popular Chinese liniment used to heal external injuries, passed down through various forms of traditional knowledge and modern science."&lt;SEP&gt;"Dit Da Jow is a traditional Chinese medicine preparation used by martial artists to aid in the healing of Iron Palm training, passed down through oral and written history."</data>
